        Update the current details so that the animation requested is the correct one
        Parameters:
        layer - The layer ID for the animation
        currentElevation - The elevation for the animation
        palette - The palette name used for the animation
        style - The style for the animation
        scaleRange - The scale range used for the animation
        nColorBands - The number of colour bands in the palette for the animation
        logScale - Whether the palette should be logarithmic
